subject: SPECIAL WARRANT - Consolidated Revenue Fund
precis: Order directing that a SPECIAL WARRANT be prepared authorizing the payment of certain sums out of the Consolidated Revenue Fund which are urgently required for the public good, for the period covering May 16, 2025 up to and including June 29, 2025.
